命還珍貴，我們今天可沒失去任何一條命。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"依Ｄ咪領袖"},{"pid":"91f8a4fdde81ca768683a4e9e0775bfe052aab23","tid":2120753,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:23:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"785220ef597fdd527607c5830aaace4dfc707adc","tid":2120753,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"黑鏡屌豬事件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}